data.description: 2 bed/2 bath Foothills charm. The lovely open floor plan features vaulted ceilings upgraded vinyl plank flooring throughout the entire home (2022), new interior paint & bath vanities. Well manicured desert landscape, fully fenced perimeter w/ high walls, full length awnings E/W of home, RV double gates & single gate, plus 2 sheds for added storage.  RV Access/parking with a Full 50 amp hookup! Pest warranty included and PRE-OWNED Solar making this energy efficient home one to make yours today!
